(727, 'Red Baron II', 'red-baron-ii', '1625248125.jpg', 1, 'Red Baron II by Dynamix, Inc is the sequel to Red Baron releases seven years prior.', '1998-10-30', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 845, NULL, NULL, 25, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-07-02 11:48:48', '2021-07-02 11:48:48'),
(726, 'The Lion King', 'the-lion-king', '1625236498.jpg', 1, 'The Lion King brings to life the majesty and mystery of Africa thruogh the tale of Simba, a lion cub faced with the challenging transition to maturity. Believing himself to be responsible for his father\'s death, Simba enters the wilderness - where he finds salvation with Pumbaa the warthog and Timon the meerkat, and his education begins. \n \nTake control of the youg cub Simba and, through interaction as detailed as the lust terrain, guide him safely through.', '1994-12-08', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3166, NULL, NULL, 25, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-07-02 08:35:02', '2021-07-02 08:35:02'),
(725, 'Disney\'s The Lion King: Simba\'s Mighty Adventure', 'disneys-the-lion-king-simbas-mighty-adventure', '1625236493.jpg', 1, 'After his father is killed, the young lion prince Simba must travel through the jungle to find his life\'s path. Eventually, he will return home and claim his rightful place as the Lion King. On his journey, Simba must avoid such dangers of the jungles and plains as wildebeests and rhinos. When he encounters these enemies as a cub, his roar does little to scare them off. However, maturing into a majestic lion deepens his voice and makes the growl useful as a weapon. As he explores the nine levels, Simba will be able to collect a wide variety of items that will open several bonuses that include puzzles, mini-games, and movies. While the film was animated in 2D, Simba and his world are rendered in three dimensions, and the plot unfolds in cinematic sequences between each level. You\'ve got to help Simba take his rightful place in DISNEY\'S THE LION KING: Simba\'s Mighty Adventure.', '2000-12-16', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 45228, NULL, NULL, 13, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-07-02 08:34:56', '2021-07-02 08:34:56'),
(724, 'Disney\'s The Lion King II: Simba\'s Pride', 'disneys-the-lion-king-ii-simbas-pride', '1625236484.jpg', 1, 'Disney\'s The Lion King II: Simba\'s Pride contains four different games: labyrinth, breakout, a rhythm game and a simple shooter. Fifty different levels are included and can be played against the computer or another player. The animations and music are based on the movie of the same name.', '1999-12-31', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 109194, NULL, NULL, 25, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-07-02 08:34:46', '2021-07-02 08:34:46'),
(723, 'Disney Classic Games: Aladdin and The Lion King', 'disney-classic-games-aladdin-and-the-lion-king', '1625236480.jpg', 1, 'Two of the most beloved Disney games of all time make their long-awaited return to modern consoles in Disney Classic Games: Aladdin and The Lion King!\nThe bundle contains different versions of these two classics:\nAladdin is playable in the Mega Drive / Genesis Version (US & Japan) and Game Boy (including a colorised variant).\nLion King is playable as Super Nintendo, Mega Drive / Genesis Version (US & Japan) and Game Boy (including a colorised variant).', '2019-10-25', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 122082, NULL, NULL, 4, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-07-02 08:34:41', '2021-07-02 08:34:41'),
