(645, 'Grand Theft Auto IV: Complete Edition', 'grand-theft-auto-iv-complete-edition', '1625138579.jpg', 1, 'This standalone retail title spans three distinct stories, interwoven to create one of the most unique and engaging single-player experiences of this generation. This definitive Grand Theft Auto bundle boasts hundreds of hours of single-player gameplay; a full suite of open-world multiplayer game types limited only by players’ creativity; dozens of eclectic radio stations with hours of music and original dialogue.', '2010-10-26', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 27912, NULL, NULL, 6, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-07-01 05:22:59', '2021-07-01 05:22:59'),
