(580, 'Call to Power II', 'call-to-power-ii', '1625136910.jpg', 1, 'Prepare to accept history\'s greatest challenge - build the world\'s most powerful empire over a span of 6,300 years, reaching from primitive history to the future realms of science-fiction. Take your place beside history\'s greatest leaders as you master the intricate strategies of governing, warfare, diplomacy, trade and science. Sow the seeds of an empire as you cultivate a tribe of settlers in 4,000 BC. Hear the cheers of approval as you lead your flourishing society into the future of 2,300 AD.', '2000-11-15', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 11266, NULL, NULL, 25, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-07-01 04:55:11', '2021-07-01 04:55:11'),
