(573, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops 4', 'call-of-duty-black-ops-4', '1625136906.jpg', 1, 'Black Ops is back! Featuring gritty, grounded, fluid Multiplayer combat, the biggest Zombies offering ever with three full undead adventures at launch, and Blackout, where the universe of Black Ops comes to life in one massive battle royale experience featuring the largest map in Call of Duty history, signature Black Ops combat, characters, locations and weapons from the entire Black Ops series.', '2018-10-12', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 83727, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-07-01 04:55:06', '2021-07-01 04:55:06'),
