(570, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops', 'call-of-duty-black-ops', '1625136904.jpg', 1, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops is the seventh main Call of Duty game and the sequel to Call of Duty: World at War. The game differs from most previous installments, which would involve a usual three-country campaign, while Call of Duty: Black Ops features two playable countries (Russia and the USA) but only has an American campaign. Several new features are also introduced, such as dive-to-prone and the available use of a flashlight on certain weapons. Furthermore, the campaign\'s playable characters now speak while being controlled by the player.', '2010-11-09', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 545, NULL, NULL, 7, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-07-01 04:55:04', '2021-07-01 04:55:04'),
