(750, 'Born of Bread', 'born-of-bread', '1626211207.jpg', 1, 'Play as a flour golem who possesses a never-ending childlike wonder and a set of odd abilities. Team-up with a colorful cast of characters, explore the different regions of a wonderful world ripe with mysteries and engage in a fun and quirky turn-based combat system.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 146525, NULL, NULL, 25, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-07-13 15:20:09', '2021-07-13 15:20:09'),
