"2300-13605\",\"id\":13605,\"length_seconds\":9683,\"deck\":\"This week we run through a stack of Nintendo news, check out Capcom beat-em-ups, remember the Intellivision, ponder the recent pinball switcheroo, break down a good air juggle, and puzzle at the name of the New York System.\",\"video_type\":\"Giant Bombcast\",\"youtube_id\":\"DYzDfzEGge0\",\"image\":\"vatar\\/36\\/366200\\/3050731-180918.jpg\"},{\"name\":\"Call of Duty: Black Ops 4\",\"api_id\":\"2300-13668\",\"id\":13668,\"length_seconds\":3380,\"deck\":\"Jeff and Ben throw a BANGER of a party and learn the importance of helmets.\",\"video_type\":\"Quick Looks\",\"youtube_id\":\"VYqDoOs63SU\",\"image\":\"vatar\\/36\\/366200\\/3055486-101218%20-%20blops.jpg\"},{\"name\":\"The Jeff Gerstmann Home Game: Call of Duty Black Ops 4\",\"api_id\":\"2300-13670\",\"id\":13670,\"length_seconds\":6116,\"deck\":\"Can I land a helicopter on another guy and kill him in Blackout? Probably. _Do_ I do that in this video? Absolutely not.\",\"video_type\":\"Features\",\"youtube_id\":\"9xZEcKx-2GI\",\"image\":\"vatar\\/0\\/26\\/3056027-vlcsnap-2018-10-15-16h19m59s186.jpg\"},{\"name\":\"554: A Nice Skin Deal\",\"api_id\":\"2300-13675\",\"id\":13675,\"length_seconds\":10843,\"deck\":\"This week we dig as deep into Black Ops IIII as humanly possible, ponder the correct boss order in Mega Man 11, puzzle at the oddities of PSN name changes, say the words \\\"Borderlands 3,\\\" and have a lengthy oatmeal chat!\",\"video_type\":\"Giant Bombcast\",\"youtube_id\":\"zXga2OaQQns\",\"image\":\"vatar\\/36\\/366200\\/3056473-123baaaaabeh.jpg\"},{\"name\":\"555: Super Mario Bros. Review\",\"api_id\":\"2300-13690\",\"id\":13690,\"length_seconds\":10941,\"deck\":\"With releases heating up, we\'re here to rate all the season\'s most important games, including Soulcalibur VI, Return of the Obra Dinn, and Black Ops 4. Plus: new old-game consoles, working at Rockstar, the goings-on at Oculus, and a lengthy look back at the old days of GameSpot.\",\"video_type\":\"Giant Bombcast\",\"youtube_id\":\"ErcTiF4twd8\",\"image\":\"vatar\\/36\\/366200\\/3058210-1827%20bc.jpg\"},{\"name\":\"562: Super Dark Souls\",\"api_id\":\"2300-13797\",\"id\":13797,\"length_seconds\":9958,\"deck\":\"This week we plow through the news bounty that dropped during the Game Awards, Smash Ultimate, the new Monster Boy, Ashen, Hades, and that new Sonic movie, uh, \\\"artwork.\\\"\",\"video_type\":\"Giant Bombcast\",\"youtube_id\":\"cIscO30yphg\",\"image\":\"vatar\\/0\\/30\\/3068588-sonic.jpg\"},{\"name\":\"563: Sopping Wet Socks\",\"api_id\":\"2300-13819\",\"id\":13819,\"length_seconds\":8608,\"deck\":\"We\'re here with the final \\\"normal\\\" Giant Bombcast of 2018, so let\'s get into some Smash Bros. unlocks, Earth Defense Force 5, Heroes of the Storm, slinging $100 copies of Kingdom Hearts III, Battlefield V, and your chicken skin-related emails!\",\"video_type\":\"Giant Bombcast\",\"youtube_id\":\"zm83b3pesek\",\"image\":\"vatar\\/36\\/366200\\/3069947-frogs%20dude.jpg\"},{\"name\":\"569: Please Tip Your Jumpmaster\",\"api_id\":\"2300-13917\",\"id\":13917,\"length_seconds\":10697,\"deck\":\"Respawn drops a new game out of nowhere and we spend a bunch of time talking about it, plus a smaller Switch, IRC memories, a world of Dr. Mario, a visit to the Strangereal, and a fresh serving of new-console speculation.\",\"video_type\":null,\"youtube_id\":\"qNIL34xVGe4\",\"image\":\"vatar\\/0\\/30\\/3079313-punching-shot-49a1b6ef81c05d449bd040251cb62fb5.jpg\"},{\"name\":\"E3 2019: It\'s Time to Hit the Beach in Call of Duty Black Ops 4\'s Days of Summer\",\"api_id\":\"2300-14513\",\"id\":14513,\"length_seconds\":60,\"deck\":\"One last hoo-rah before Modern Warfare hits.\",\"video_type\":\"Trailers\",\"youtube_id\":0,\"image\":\"vatar\\/0\\/1992\\/3107419-screen%20shot%202019-06-11%20at%208.51.55%20pm.jpg\"},{\"name\":\"590: Ice Cube Is Our Coworker\",\"api_id\":\"2300-14619\",\"id\":14619,\"length_seconds\":9262,\"deck\":\"This week\'s hot topics include Mario Maker 2, CEO, console tariffs, the PUBG \\\"universe,\\\" the Black Ops 4 that could have been, a variety of chicken\\/waffle configurations, Barenaked pinball, and the origin of inverted castles.\",\"video_type\":\"Giant Bombcast\",\"youtube_id\":\"rOo20VfddVg\",\"image\":\"vatar\\/0\\/30\\/3111734-qkimuav%5B1%5D.jpg\"}]', '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL),
