\":\"BQa2NFVNskE\",\"image\":\"vatar\\/0\\/31\\/3192951-8983760837-18060.jpg\"},{\"name\":\"635: S-rank With Your Coffee Dad\",\"api_id\":\"2300-15627\",\"id\":15627,\"length_seconds\":10211,\"deck\":\"This week we welcome back Brad (and the tales of his nose), dig and craft in Minecraft and Terraria, gawk at that Unreal Engine 5 demo, speculate about Ghost of Tsushima and the new Paper Mario, debate video game rap battles and esports rules, and enter a straw-hole paradox from which we may never return.\",\"video_type\":\"Giant Bombcast\",\"youtube_id\":\"Jy6-1fkhp2Q\",\"image\":\"vatar\\/0\\/30\\/3193998-background.jpg\"},{\"name\":\"Episode 269\",\"api_id\":\"2300-15913\",\"id\":15913,\"length_seconds\":8564,\"deck\":\"We\'re back and we\'ve got impressions of Ghost of Tsushima, Paper Mario: The Origami King, Assassin\'s Creed Valhalla, and Watch Dogs: Legion! Games! Also, some news, your emails, and more!\",\"video_type\":null,\"youtube_id\":\"xCOt5VIYhlI\",\"image\":\"vatar\\/0\\/31\\/3220938-beastcast_07162020.jpg\"},{\"name\":\"Paper Mario: The Origami King\",\"api_id\":\"2300-15928\",\"id\":15928,\"length_seconds\":2967,\"deck\":\"We attempt to line up and arrange ourselves for the perfect chance to look at this charming and fun Mario romp.\",\"video_type\":\"Quick Looks\",\"youtube_id\":\"21GgAGx25G4\",\"image\":\"vatar\\/0\\/31\\/3224982-papermaio_origamiking.jpg\"},{\"name\":\"644: WarioWare Without the Wario\",\"api_id\":\"2300-15932\",\"id\":15932,\"length_seconds\":8886,\"deck\":\"Tamoor Hussain pops over from GameSpot to talk samurai photography, the new Paper Mario, the current whereabouts of Francis York Morgan, the latest goings-on with next-gen consoles, the great charge-move controversy, and stealing booze from monkeys.\",\"video_type\":null,\"youtube_id\":\"msy9daqrRiI\",\"image\":\"vatar\\/0\\/30\\/3225055-emvca76wwaeaxpw_format%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium.jpg\"},{\"name\":\"Episode 270\",\"api_id\":\"2300-15958\",\"id\":15958,\"length_seconds\":9446,\"deck\":\"Ben Pack joins us to talk about Paper Mario: The Origami King, Microsoft\'s latest not-E3 showing for their upcoming games, and much more!\",\"video_type\":null,\"youtube_id\":\"PTMB39qpeRw\",\"image\":\"vatar\\/0\\/31\\/3226371-beastcast_07242020.jpg\"},{\"name\":\"645: Evidence of Luigi\",\"api_id\":\"2300-15968\",\"id\":15968,\"length_seconds\":10818,\"deck\":\"As July comes to a close we recap Microsoft\'s latest Xbox Series X Event, continued adventures in Ghost of Tsushima, catching rare monsters in Pokemon Go Fest 2020, dipping stuff in other stuff, leaks at Nintendo, G4 coming back, and the long awaited sequel: Meme Run 2.\",\"video_type\":\"Giant Bombcast\",\"youtube_id\":\"N38zfmrFKbM\",\"image\":\"vatar\\/36\\/366200\\/3228901-bc072820.jpg\"},{\"name\":\"Episode 273\",\"api_id\":\"2300-16058\",\"id\":16058,\"length_seconds\":9020,\"deck\":\"Did you know Halo Infinite has been delayed? It\'s true. Did you know Epic and Apple are fighting? They are. Did you know there\'s a bird that maybe eats flamingos? I\'m still unclear on this.\",\"video_type\":null,\"youtube_id\":\"Xz-UxQvymNc\",\"image\":\"vatar\\/0\\/31\\/3234666-beastcast_273.jpg\"}]', '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL),
