VIYhlI\",\"image\":\"vatar\\/0\\/31\\/3220938-beastcast_07162020.jpg\"},{\"name\":\"658: Geometry Wars 99\",\"api_id\":\"2300-16287\",\"id\":16287,\"length_seconds\":9968,\"deck\":\"The PlayStation 5 is here, and we\'re also here to talk about the DualSense controller and Cooling Springs in Astro\'s Playroom, along with Watch Dogs Legion, Immortals Fenyx Rising, our wishlist for next-gen Geometry Wars, the Uncharted movie cast, and the many uses for that indelible Crown Royal bag.\",\"video_type\":\"Giant Bombcast\",\"youtube_id\":\"_19WE3Rpu4o\",\"image\":\"vatar\\/0\\/30\\/3251225-vlcsnap-2020-10-27-14h41m58s232.jpg\"},{\"name\":\"Breakfast \'n Brad: Watch Dogs Legion\",\"api_id\":\"2300-16294\",\"id\":16294,\"length_seconds\":4322,\"deck\":\"This cyber-dystopia is a real bummer. Let\'s fix it!\",\"video_type\":\"Features\",\"youtube_id\":\"uCahqzzcD9Y\",\"image\":\"vatar\\/0\\/30\\/3251568-vlcsnap-2020-10-29-10h47m50s892.jpg\"},{\"name\":\"Episode 284\",\"api_id\":\"2300-16296\",\"id\":16296,\"length_seconds\":8421,\"deck\":\"So much to get through. Amnesia: Rebirth, Transformers: Battlegrounds, Dark Pictures: Little Hope and even a bit about that PS5 and its controller! We\'ve also got news, emails, and more!\",\"video_type\":null,\"youtube_id\":\"-wxBZvnV-uw\",\"image\":\"vatar\\/0\\/31\\/3251593-vf_thegiantbeastcast_ep289_vinny.jpg\"},{\"name\":\"659: \\u0f3c \\u3064 \\u25d5_\\u25d5 \\u0f3d\\u3064\",\"api_id\":\"2300-16310\",\"id\":16310,\"length_seconds\":8784,\"deck\":\"This week: our first thoughts on the Xbox Series X and S, the magical destruction of Teardown, the breakneck cyber-parkour of Ghostrunner, more time with Watch Dogs: Legion, looking back on the big overnight game launches of yore, Sony throws cold water on PSVR and PS5 faceplates, and more than a few of your emails!\",\"video_type\":null,\"youtube_id\":\"TG65wDPVEg8\",\"image\":\"vatar\\/0\\/30\\/3252370-halo7-111.jpg\"},{\"name\":\"Console Launchapalooza: The Xbox Series X\",\"api_id\":\"2300-16350\",\"id\":16350,\"length_seconds\":9186,\"deck\":\"Let\'s check out that new Xbox and all those new and upgraded games now that everything is on shelves.\",\"video_type\":null,\"youtube_id\":\"z1Lo_uTJLUA\",\"image\":\"vatar\\/0\\/30\\/3254088-vlcsnap-2020-11-11-16h31m55s131.jpg\"},{\"name\":\"662: Turn the Musou Crank\",\"api_id\":\"2300-16394\",\"id\":16394,\"length_seconds\":9444,\"deck\":\"We\'re settling into the new post-console-launch normal with more time on the PS5 and XSX and their games, the closing chapters of Yakuza: Like a Dragon, the million-moblin action of Hyrule Warriors: Age of Calamity, Kingdom Hearts except a rhythm game, Street Fighters and Mortal Kombats old and new, Nintendo and the RIAA getting litigious again, plus the rarely seen but always refreshing three-mails.\",\"video_type\":\"Giant Bombcast\",\"youtube_id\":\"CNnEUvH_SNY\",\"image\":\"vatar\\/0\\/30\\/3256318-vlcsnap-2020-11-24-14h37m59s987.jpg\"}]', '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL),
