(82550, 'Dwarven Brawl Bros', 'Dwarven Brawl Bros is a local 2 to 6 player 2D fighting (brawling) game with a retroish feel. Play as a dwarf and kill your bros! Fast-paced brawling in all-vs-all and team settings with 31 weapons, 38 stages, 26 game modes!', 'footbal', '', '[{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/y8caircmoezrujiegzlv.jpg\",\"tags\":\"All Images\",\"image_id\":\"y8caircmoezrujiegzlv\"},{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/qpflu0yetnsgejrztryj.jpg\",\"tags\":\"All Images\",\"image_id\":\"qpflu0yetnsgejrztryj\"},{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/qgdd5sqxyxmir479im7w.jpg\",\"tags\":\"All Images\",\"image_id\":\"qgdd5sqxyxmir479im7w\"},{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/f11fsvqur76fzejyjuxq.jpg\",\"tags\":\"All Images\",\"image_id\":\"f11fsvqur76fzejyjuxq\"},{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/kvbmvc3ftcnygdbeoowd.jpg\",\"tags\":\"All Images\",\"image_id\":\"kvbmvc3ftcnygdbeoowd\"}]', '', NULL, NULL, '2021-05-24 17:09:15', '2021-05-24 17:09:15'),
(82551, 'Dolmen', 'No innovation was made without a crazy idea. And Dolmen is both things! On development by Massive Work Studio, it’s an adult videogame, an Action third person RPG, where the player’s worst fears turn against him, finding the aberrant alien world of Revion Prime. \n \nIn a bold initiative in Brazil Games Industry, this studio, after one year of research and preparation is going to launch a crowdfunding campaign through the Kickstarter platform and show a little bit of the first phase of its work in the tenth edition of Brasil Game Show! \n \nThe gamer community and fans have had the first samples of what is still to come since september 23, when exclusive info and pics begun to spread from social medias as facebook, twitter, youtube and instagram. \n \nWith periodic posts, the staff will give its followers the rare opportunity to get inside the creative minds of the artists as if they visited some painter’s atelier, providing the potential campaign supporters with a nice view of the mind of more than 40 collaborators, among brazilian, iranian, american and spanish people! \n \nWe are very proud to show this work to its public as also to display its possibilities to the actual gamers’ generation. They will surely start a new experience in a future brought a little closer to us thanks to the world of the Indie Games!', 'footbal', 'ex5rocyhbx2tdeo84bmw', '[{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/sc6wq6.jpg\",\"tags\":\"All Images\",\"image_id\":\"sc6wq6\"},{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/sc6wq7.jpg\",\"tags\":\"All Images\",\"image_id\":\"sc6wq7\"},{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/sc6wq8.jpg\",\"tags\":\"All Images\",\"image_id\":\"sc6wq8\"},{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/sc6wq9.jpg\",\"tags\":\"All Images\",\"image_id\":\"sc6wq9\"},{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/sc6