(82609, 'Chivalry 2', 'Chivalry 2 is a multiplayer first-person slasher inspired by epic medieval movie battles. Players are thrust into the action of every iconic moment of the era - from the thunder of cavalry charges to storms of flaming arrows, sprawling castle sieges and more.\n\nImproving on the original genre-defining Chivalry: Medieval Warfare, Chivalry 2 invites players to master the blade with an all-new and improved combat system that combines real-time strikes and a free-flowing combo system to speed up the action and let players become a whirlwind of steel on the battlefield. Created with the ability to fight multiple foes in mind, Chivalry 2’s combat mixes the best of both FPS and fighting game genres for an unmatched melee experience.', 'footbal', 'co2yqh', '[{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/sc6lfl.jpg\",\"tags\":\"All Images\",\"image_id\":\"sc6lfl\"},{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/sc6lfm.jpg\",\"tags\":\"All Images\",\"image_id\":\"sc6lfm\"},{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/sc6lfn.jpg\",\"tags\":\"All Images\",\"image_id\":\"sc6lfn\"},{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/sc6lfo.jpg\",\"tags\":\"All Images\",\"image_id\":\"sc6lfo\"},{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/sc6lfp.jpg\",\"tags\":\"All Images\",\"image_id\":\"sc6lfp\"},{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/sc6lfq.jpg\",\"tags\":\"All Images\",\"image_id\":\"sc6lfq\"}]', '[{\"name\":\"Chivalry 2\",\"api_id\":\"123\",\"id\":296,\"length_seconds\":\"12345\",\"deck\":\"Chivalry 2\",\"video_type\":\"Trailers\",\"0\":\"\",\"youtube_id\":\"ESPXnkkx1rA\",\"image\":\"vatar\\\\\\/mig\\\\\\/0\\\\\\/9\\\\\\/2\\\\\\/5\\\\\\/3400925-trailer_maneater_reveal_20180612.jpg\"},{\"name\":\"Chivalry 2\",\"api_id\":\"123\",\"id\":296,\"length_seconds\":\"12345\",\"deck\":\"Chivalry 2\",\"video_type