(82635, 'Necromunda: Hired Gun', 'Pick your contracts. Hunt your targets. Collect the bounty.\n\nNavigate an ocean of crime and corruption to balance the bloody ecosystem of Necromunda as a merciless hired gun. The money’s good, the dog’s loyal, and the gun’s reliable – but can you survive the hunt? Necromunda: Hired Gun is an indie fast-paced, violent, and thrilling FPS set in the darkest reaches of Warhammer 40,000’s most infamous hive city.\n\nFor the right price, eliminate the most notorious gangers and mutants. Your armory is a sprawling arsenal. Your body is enhanced with a dozen customizable augments to run on walls and leap over chasms. Your cyber-mastiff will sniff out and kill enemies for you, while your grappling hook allows quick, agile traversal of the massive environments.\n\n- An indie fast-paced FPS in the Warhammer 40,000 universe\n- Upgrade and fight alongside your loyal cyber-mastiff\n- Endless weapon and augment customization\n- Upgrade, advance, and level up as you collect bounties', 'footbal', 'co31dd', '[{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/sc95cb.jpg\",\"tags\":\"All Images\",\"image_id\":\"sc95cb\"},{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/sc95cc.jpg\",\"tags\":\"All Images\",\"image_id\":\"sc95cc\"},{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/sc95cd.jpg\",\"tags\":\"All Images\",\"image_id\":\"sc95cd\"},{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/sc95ce.jpg\",\"tags\":\"All Images\",\"image_id\":\"sc95ce\"},{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/sc95cf.jpg\",\"tags\":\"All Images\",\"image_id\":\"sc95cf\"}]', '', '', 'IGDB', '2021-05-31 12:41:04', '2021-05-31 12:41:04'),
(82636, 'Chivalry 2', 'Chivalry 2 is a multiplayer first-person slasher inspired by epic medieval movie battles. Players are thrust into the action of every iconic moment of the era - from the thunder of cavalry charges to storms of flaming arrows, sprawling castle sieges and more.\n\nImproving on the original genre-defining Chivalry: Medieval Warfare, Chivalry 2 invites players to master the blade with an all-new and improved combat system that combines real-time strikes and a free-flowing combo system to speed up the action and let players become a whirlwind of steel on the battlefield. Created with the ability to fight multiple foes in mind, Chivalry 2’s combat mixes the best of both FPS and fighting game genres for an unmatched melee experience.', 'footbal', 'co2yqh', '[{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/sc6lfl.jpg\",\"tags\":\"All Images\",\"image_id\":\"sc6lfl\"},{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/sc6lfm.jpg\",\"tags\":\"All Images\",\"image_id\":\"sc6lfm\"},{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/sc6lfn.jpg\",\"tags\":\"All Images\",\"image_id\":\"sc6lfn\"},{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/sc6lfo.jpg\",\"tags\":\"All Images\",\"image_id\":\"sc6lfo\"},{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/sc6lfp.jpg\",\"tags\":\"All Images\",\"image_id\":\"sc6lfp\"},{\"image\":\"\\/\\/images.igdb.com\\/igdb\\/image\\/upload\\/t_thumb\\/sc6lfq.jpg\",\"tags\":\"All Images\",\"image_id\":\"sc6lfq\"}]', '[{\"name\":\"Chivalry 2\",\"api_id\":\"123\",\"id\":375,\"length_seconds\":\"12345\",\"deck\":\"Chivalry 2\",\"video_type\":\"Trailers\",\"0\":\"\",\"youtube_id\":\"ESPXnkkx1rA\",\"image\":\"vatar\\\\\\/mig\\\\\\/0\\\\\\/9\\\\\\/2\\\\\\/5\\\\\\/3400925-trailer_maneater_reveal_20180612.jpg\"},{\"name\":\"Chivalry 2\",\"api_id\":\"123\",\"id\":375,\"length_seconds\":\"12345\",\"deck\":\"Chivalry 2\",\"video_type