(13, 13, 'Brotherhood United', NULL, NULL, 'https://static.metacritic.com/images/products/games/9/6725c09bf5b95522e0a0845c773a2690-98.jpg', 'When the time of crisis comes and one of your friends is captured, you gotta stand your ground and fight for your partners. When someone messes with the brotherhood, you make sure they pay for that, no matter what. Pick your guns and blast your way through hordes of enemies on this run and gun game as a member of the Brotherhood who leaves no friend behind.', '[\"Action\",\"Platformer\",\"2D\"]', 'Switch', 'Silesia Games', 'Myoubouh Corp', 'M', '2020-03-12', 'http://www.metacritic.com/game/switch/brotherhood-united', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(14, 14, 'Foregone', NULL, NULL, 'https://static.metacritic.com/images/products/games/4/a6e09a315838172cbe0c950079c0e31f-98.jpg', 'Foregone has players take on the role of the city of Calagan’s strongest Arbiter, tasked with investigating the sudden resurgence of an all-corrupting force known as the Harrow. The Arbiter will destroy legions of enemies, battle formidable bosses, and collect a wide array of upgradeable loot as she embarks on a twisted journey to unravel the haunting truth behind the Harrow. The intense, combat-focused title features fluid pixel artwork, combining old-school visual influences with modern 3D animation technology.', '[\"Action\",\"Platformer\",\"2D\"]', 'Xbox One', 'Big Blue Bubble Inc.', 'Big Blue Bubble Inc.', '', '2020-10-13', 'http://www.metacritic.com/game/xbox-one/foregone', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(15, 15, 'COLLAPSED', NULL, 83, 'https://static.metacritic.com/images/products/games/8/5969345b6f488bc325bab22e47b1bcd3-98.jpg', 'Collapsed is a roguelike platformer set in a post-apocalyptic world. Innumerable hordes of bloodthirsty aliens have crossed the borders of our Solar System, intent upon enslaving all sentient life in the universe. Capturing planet after planet, the aliens make their way to Earth, where they face stiff resistance: Earthlings have learned how to fight back against the invaders and have created a powerful weapon. You play as one of four Hunters (each with their own set of abilities, skills and combat style) and work to annihilate the extraterrestrials who’ve landed on the planet. Clear numerous unique locations with procedurally generated levels, hordes of dangerous enemies, and deadly traps. Combat in heated battles will test your skills and reaction time.', '[\"Action\",\"Platformer\",\"2D\"]', 'Switch', 'OverGamez', 'Glaive Games', '', '2020-08-29', 'http://www.metacritic.com/game/switch/collapsed', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(16, 16, 'Hero Must Die. Again', NULL, 75, 'https://static.metacritic.com/images/products/games/7/ae9cd724fd6b67e97f1df48644cec233-98.jpg', '', '[\"Role-Playing\",\"Japanese-Style\"]', 'Switch', 'Degica', 'G-mode', 'T', '2020-02-27', 'http://www.metacritic.com/game/switch/hero-must-die-again', NULL, NULL, NULL),
