(94, 94, 'God of War III Remastered', NULL, 82, 'https://static.metacritic.com/images/products/games/8/6ce4198d741ddf89d12715a3b25dcc20-98.jpg', 'Originally developed by SCE Santa Monica Studio for the PS3, God of War 3 has been remastered for the PS4 and gameplay supports 1080p at 60fps. God of War 3 Remastered brings epic battles to life with graphics and an elaborate plot that put Kratos at the center of carnage and destruction as he pursues revenge against the Gods who have betrayed him. Set in the realm of brutal Greek mythology, God of War 3 Remastered is the single-player game that allows players to assume the fearless role of the ex-Spartan warrior, Kratos, as he rises from the darkest depths of Hades to scale the very heights of Mount Olympus to seek his bloody revenge. Armed with double-chained blades and an array of new weapons and magic, Kratos must take on mythology’s deadliest creatures while solving intricate puzzles throughout his merciless quest to destroy Olympus.', '[\"Action Adventure\",\"Linear\"]', 'PlayStation 4', 'SCEA', 'Wholesale Algorithms', 'M', '2015-07-14', 'http://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-4/god-of-war-iii-remastered', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(95, 95, 'Cozy Grove', NULL, 88, 'https://static.metacritic.com/images/products/games/9/50f8de06e9220d0b4e0d9d7044106c89-98.jpg', 'Welcome to Cozy Grove, a life-sim game about camping on a haunted, ever-changing island. As a Spirit Scout, you\'ll wander the island\'s forest each day, finding new hidden secrets and helping soothe the local ghosts. With a little time and a lot of crafting, you\'ll bring color and joy back to Cozy Grove!Features:* Beautiful, dynamic, hand-drawn landscapes that come alive when you help a spirit in need.* Dozens of memorable characters and spirits for you to find and befriend. Each spirit has a unique, extensive story for you to unravel over time.* Collect spirit animals, craft decorations, go fishing and more!* 40+ hour campaign filled with side quests, designed to span months of playtime.', '[\"Adventure\",\"General\"]', 'Switch', 'The Quantum Astrophysicists Guild', 'Spry Fox', '', '2021-04-08', 'http://www.metacritic.com/game/switch/cozy-grove', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(96, 96, 'AER: Memories of Old', NULL, 64, 'https://static.metacritic.com/images/products/games/5/873a2a6d4e9dce6fd9c445ea5b951ef1-98.jpg', '', '[\"Action Adventure\",\"Open-World\"]', 'Switch', 'Daedalic Entertainment', 'Daedalic Entertainment', 'E10+', '2019-08-28', 'http://www.metacritic.com/game/switch/aer-memories-of-old', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(97, 97, 'The Legend of Zelda: Skyward Sword HD', NULL, NULL, 'https://static.metacritic.com/images/products/games/2/1f9fc183e00b8ded06c79eadf957c281-98.jpg', 'Take to the skies, draw your sword, and experience the earliest story in the Legend of Zelda series. Join Link in his high-flying quest to save Zelda, a childhood friend who must confront her destiny. Soar between floating islands and descend to the treacherous surface world in this updated HD version of the Legend of Zelda: Skyward Sword. Master realistic swordplay that matches your movements. Swing your sword and angle your slashes to uncover and break through opponents’ defenses using intuitive motion controls. Link will match the angle of each strike you make with the Joy-Con controller, creating immersive swordplay that relies on strategy and accuracy. Movements feel smoother and more immediate thanks to the Nintendo Switch system’s increased processing power and HD graphics. Take advantage of the newly-added button only control scheme—perfect for playing in handheld mode or on the Nintendo Switch Lite system.', '[\"Action Adventure\",\"Open-World\"]', 'Switch', 'Nintendo', 'Nintendo', 'E10+', '2021-07-16', 'http://www.metacritic.com/game/switch/the-legend-of-zelda-skyward-sword-hd', NULL, NULL, NULL),
