(110, 110, 'The Dark Pictures Anthology: Little Hope', NULL, 69, 'https://static.metacritic.com/images/products/games/4/1a406caa1256b9ca862b98ecd6ffde1f-98.jpg', 'Abandoned and all alone, 4 college students and their teacher become stranded in an isolated town miles from anywhere after their bus crashes in bad weather. Trapped by a mysterious fog in the town of Little Hope, they search desperately for a means of escape whilst visions from the past haunt them from the shadows. \r\rKey features:\r\rWELCOME TO LITTLE HOPE\rWitness terrifying visions of the past, haunted by the events of the XVIIth century Andover Witch Trials.\r\rSAVE YOUR SOULS...\rEscape the nightmarish apparitions that relentlessly pursue your cast\r\rDON\'T PLAY ALONE\rPlay online with a friend or up to 5 friends offline, share your story and cooperate wisely to save your cast.\r\rAbandon Hope All who enter here', '[\"Action Adventure\",\"Survival\"]', 'PC', 'Bandai Namco Games', 'Supermassive Games', 'M', '2020-10-30', 'http://www.metacritic.com/game/pc/the-dark-pictures-anthology-little-hope', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(111, 111, 'The Dark Pictures Anthology: Little Hope', NULL, 69, 'https://static.metacritic.com/images/products/games/4/1a406caa1256b9ca862b98ecd6ffde1f-98.jpg', 'Abandoned and all alone, 4 college students and their teacher become stranded in an isolated town miles from anywhere after their bus crashes in bad weather. Trapped by a mysterious fog in the town of Little Hope, they search desperately for a means of escape whilst visions from the past haunt them from the shadows. \r\rKey features:\r\rWELCOME TO LITTLE HOPE\rWitness terrifying visions of the past, haunted by the events of the XVIIth century Andover Witch Trials.\r\rSAVE YOUR SOULS...\rEscape the nightmarish apparitions that relentlessly pursue your cast\r\rDON\'T PLAY ALONE\rPlay online with a friend or up to 5 friends offline, share your story and cooperate wisely to save your cast.\r\rAbandon Hope All who enter here', '[\"Action Adventure\",\"Survival\"]', 'PC', 'Bandai Namco Games', 'Supermassive Games', 'M', '2020-10-30', 'http://www.metacritic.com/game/pc/the-dark-pictures-anthology-little-hope', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(112, 112, 'Horror Adventure', NULL, NULL, 'https://static.metacritic.com/images/products/games/4/7ff6d136fad4c69f8a01d72a53f877c0-98.jpg', 'Horror Adventure is a interactive experience set in a procedurally generated haunted house. You\'re a paranormal investigator and you find yourself exploring what appears to be a old abandoned manor.\r\rYou will be able to interact with basic items and limited tools at your disposal. The procedurally generated random house will create random locations and scares for you. So make sure to keep your eyes open at all the times, put your headphones on and enjoy the game!', '[\"Action Adventure\",\"Survival\"]', 'PlayStation 4', 'Yash Future Tech Solutions Pvt Ltd', 'Yash Future Tech Solutions Pvt Ltd', '', '2020-08-14', 'http://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-4/horror-adventure', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(113, 113, 'New Pokemon Snap', NULL, NULL, 'https://static.metacritic.com/images/products/games/5/b7815b5721b4de77b89ee9e01613ba90-98.jpg', 'Photograph Pokémon in their natural habitats as you adventure through unknown islands!\r\rSeek out and take in-game pictures of Pokémon in their native environments in the New Pokémon Snap game, only for the Nintendo Switch system! You\'ll even discover behaviors and expressions you\'ve never seen before when you encounter and research lively wild Pokémon.\r\rExplore environments, take in-game pictures and fill your Pokémon Photodex\r\rTravel to unknown islands with beautiful scenery like lush jungles and sandy beaches. The Pokémon pictures you take there will be used to build your very own Pokémon Photodex!\r\rThis brand-new game brings the gameplay of the 1999 Pokémon Snap game for the Nintendo 64 system to life on the Nintendo Switch system with unknown islands to discover and different Pokémon to see!\r\rPhotograph lively wild Pokémon in their natural habitats as you research and explore unknown islands. Journey through a variety of environments such as beaches and jungles to capture previously-unseen Pokémon behaviors. The photos you take can also be used to fill out your very own Pokémon Photodex!\r\r* See a different side of Pokémon in a new photo-snapping adventure, only on Nintendo Switch\r* Research various Pokémon in their natural habitats and capture Pokémon behaviors that you\'ve never seen before\r* Explore unknown islands with scenery like lush jungles and tropical beaches throughout your journey\r* Take in-game photos to make your very own Pokémon Photodex', '[\"Action\",\"Shooter\",\"Rail\"]', 'Switch', 'Nintendo\n                                                    \n\n                                                        The Pokemon Company', 'Bandai Namco Games, The Pokemon Company', 'E', '2021-04-30', 'http://www.metacritic.com/game/switch/new-pokemon-snap', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(114, 114, 'Far Cry 6', NULL, NULL, 'https://static.metacritic.com/images/products/games/5/d8033f939f9897b221d25f0324cdf4a6-98.jpg', 'Far Cry 6 reveals a Caribbean island simmering with revolutionary tension. The title features actor Giancarlo Esposito (“Better Call Saul,” “The Boys,” “The Mandalorian”) as President Anton Castillo, the violent leader who grips the island of Yara with an iron fist, promising a return to its former glory. With an arsenal of weapons and allies at your back, you’ll take on Castillo’s regime and fight for the future of Yara. As Dani Rojas (playable as a female or male character), you will help stoke the fires of revolution through guerrilla warfare across the island of Yara, from verdant jungles to the urban streets of the capital city, Esperanza. You’ll use a powerful array of weapons and vehicles, and build a network of allies to fight alongside you, including Fangs for Hire like Chorizo, the dangerously distracting wiener dog. As President Castillo prepares his son Diego, played by Anthony Gonzalez (“Coco”), to succeed him, you will do all you can to ensure his plans don’t come to fruition. [Ubisoft]', '[\"Action Adventure\",\"Open-World\"]', 'PC', 'Ubisoft', 'Ubisoft Toronto', '', '2022-01-01', 'http://www.metacritic.com/game/pc/far-cry-6', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(115, 115, 'Balan Wonderworld', NULL, 86, 'https://static.metacritic.com/images/products/games/3/c73a9dcaceea213e5d1557a13fde0aca-98.jpg', 'Balan Wonderworld is a wondrous action-platformer game themed around a mysterious musical theatre. The stars of the show will use special abilities from a multitude of characterful costumes as they adventure in the bizarre and imaginary land of Wonderworld. Here memories and vistas from the real world mix with the things that people hold dear. Twelve different tales await our stars in Wonderworld, each with their own unique quirks. They will explore all corners of these labyrinthine stages, using all the tricks and gimmicks hidden along the way, to get to the heart of each touching story.', '[\"Action\",\"Platformer\",\"3D\"]', 'Xbox One', 'Square Enix', 'Square Enix, Arzest, Balan Company', 'E10+', '2021-03-26', 'http://www.metacritic.com/game/xbox-one/balan-wonderworld', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(116, 116, 'Alvo', NULL, NULL, 'https://static.metacritic.com/images/products/games/3/25f410ea9297edcf146e431182a49ed4-98.jpg', 'Squad up with new or existing friends and utilize the in-game voice chat to strategize your next move. Are you going to hold one location or attack the enemy in a run-and-gun style? The choice is yours. Filled with heated combat, explosions, and tactical gameplay there’s something here for everyone. Enlist in the ALVO army today!\r\rKEY FEATURES\r\rINSTANT ACTION- The implementation of a dedicated server and dynamic empty-space bot filled lobby system, you are in the battle within seconds after joining friends for a smooth and constant state of play.\r\rFREEDOM OF MOVEMENT-ALVO allows you to fire weapons and launch grenades while running, jumping, climbing, crouching, sliding, and even while prone, creating a VR experience like no other.\r\rCUSTOMIZATION-With its large array of options customization, you can manipulate the gun offset to your personal specifications. Change your HUD to show or hide visual information from the well-integrated UI, or play around with the audio and comfort settings to give you the best immersive experience', '[\"Action\",\"Shooter\",\"First-Person\",\"Tactical\"]', 'PlayStation 4', 'Mardonpol Inc.', 'Mardonpol Inc.', '', '2021-04-13', 'http://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-4/alvo', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(117, 131, 'Smelter', NULL, NULL, 'https://static.metacritic.com/images/products/games/8/281b602a8d5faf9370b2f5e3ab06b9a7-98.jpg', 'Time To Get Eve’n\r\rYou are Eve, fresh out of Eden and armed with a living suit of armor. Explore a dangerous new world, battle its bizarre denizens and expand your empire in a desperate journey to find Adam.\r\rSmelter is a strategy, action-platformer combo inspired by classics from the 16-bit era. Lead Smelter and his faithful Zirm forces by expanding Smelter’s territory across the Rumbly Lands in top-down strategy levels, then dive into thrilling side-scrolling action stages after annexing key locations. Build, attack and advance your army -- unlock, upgrade and unleash elemental action skills against vicious enemies, perilous environments and dangerous bosses. Release the power of Smelter!\r\rSTORY\rAfter the untimely destruction of the Garden, Eve finds herself in an unfamiliar world with her beloved Adam nowhere to be found. In her search for Adam, she encounters Smelter, an unusually over-confident, winged creature with the powerful ability to transform and fuse with others, giving them incredible powers.\r\rOffering his apparently “invaluable” assistance, Smelter transforms and fuses with Eve. They depart on a journey to the treacherous Rumbly Lands. There, they expand Smelter’s territory, allowing them to reach further into the various domains to find out what happened to her Adam, hoping to find him in one piece and find a way back home to their peaceful lives...', '[\"Strategy\",\"Real-Time\",\"General\"]', 'Switch', 'DANGEN Entertainment', 'X Plus', '', '2021-04-22', 'http://www.metacritic.com/game/switch/smelter', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(118, 132, 'Rhythm Doctor', NULL, NULL, 'https://static.metacritic.com/images/products/games/98w-game.jpg', 'Save lives with your spacebar!Rhythm Doctor is a rhythm game in a world where defibrillating patients\' hearts in sync with their heartbeats has healing properties. Slam your spacebar in perfect time on the 7th beat, and they might just come out okay. But beware - every patient has unique illnesses based on complex music theory: polyrhythms, hemiolas, irregular time signatures...if you don\'t know what they mean, don\'t worry. Rhythm Doctor is designed to make you learn music and rhythm theory without even realising it!', '[\"Action\",\"Rhythm\",\"Music\"]', 'Switch', '7th Beat Games', '7th Beat Games', '', '2022-01-01', 'http://www.metacritic.com/game/switch/rhythm-doctor', NULL, NULL, NULL);
