(193, 378, 'Dying Light 2', NULL, 0, 'co1qr0', 'The last great human settlement exists within an unforgiving, infected world. Exceptional agility and combat skills make you a powerful ally and a valuable commodity. With your unique abilities you have the power to be an agent of change within this decaying metropolis. Use it wisely.', NULL, 'PlayStation 4', 'IGDB', 'IGDB', 'M', '0000-00-00', 'https://www.igdb.com/games/dying-light-2', 'IGDB', '2021-05-31 16:00:50', '2021-05-31 16:00:50'),
