(197, 382, 'The Elder Scrolls Online: Blackwood', NULL, 0, 'co2usv', 'A deal made with the Prince of Destruction comes due in The Elder Scrolls Online: Blackwood, part of the Gates of Oblivion adventure. Explore Imperial cities and murky bogs, uncover Mehrunes Dagon\'s sinister plot, and never adventure alone with the new Companions System.', NULL, 'Xbox One', 'IGDB', 'IGDB', 'M', '0000-00-00', 'https://www.igdb.com/games/the-elder-scrolls-online-blackwood', 'IGDB', '2021-06-01 14:47:06', '2021-06-01 14:47:06'),
(198, 383, 'Hit N \'Rush', NULL, 0, 'co2sg7', 'Hit n´Rush is a third person multiplayer Battle Royale shooter playing in an post-apocalyptic future on planet earth. Choose your character, the Rusher, to compete against other Rushers and fight against mutants, Rovers. Loot the best weapons and find shelter from the deadly pulse.', NULL, 'PC (Microsoft Windows)', 'IGDB', 'IGDB', 'M', '0000-00-00', 'https://www.igdb.com/games/hit-n-rush', 'IGDB', '2021-06-01 14:57:47', '2021-06-01 14:57:47'),
(199, 384, 'Scavengers', NULL, 0, 'co2yd7', 'Scavengers is your strategic survival battleground. Enter a free-to-play action shooter where squads of three compete to survive and dominate in a hybrid of sandbox-style PVE and class-based PVP. Choose from a roster of adaptive Explorers, arm yourself with a combination of unique abilities and weapons, and conquer the challenges of a hostile wasteland. Outthink and outfight enemy players and the dwellers of the frozen Earth.', NULL, 'PC (Microsoft Windows)', 'IGDB', 'IGDB', 'M', '0000-00-00', 'https://www.igdb.com/games/scavengers', 'IGDB', '2021-06-01 14:59:49', '2021-06-01 14:59:49'),
(200, 385, 'Until We Die', NULL, 0, 'co30gp', 'Until We Die is a post-apocalyptic strategy game where the remains of survivors took refuge in the Moscow Underground after a global disaster. Command wards to gather supplies and turn an abandoned station into an impregnable fortress-colony capable of resisting any threat.', NULL, 'PC (Microsoft Windows)', 'IGDB', 'IGDB', 'M', '0000-00-00', 'https://www.igdb.com/games/until-we-die', 'IGDB', '2021-06-01 15:07:02', '2021-06-01 15:07:02'),
(201, 386, 'Returnal', NULL, 86, 'co2jfc', 'Returnal combines action with roguelike gameplay into a third-person shooter where players fight to survive a hostile planet that changes with every death. Players can switch instinctively between firing modes by using a single adaptive trigger and can get right back into the action after dying. PS5\'s immersive 3D audio brings the alien world to life around the player, helping players navigate the intense positional combat.', NULL, 'PlayStation 5', 'IGDB', 'IGDB', 'M', '0000-00-00', 'https://www.igdb.com/games/returnal', 'IGDB', '2021-06-01 15:11:39', '2021-06-01 15:11:39'),
(202, 387, 'Syberia: The World Before', NULL, 0, 'co2idt', 'Embark on a journey across continents and through time, as you piece together the puzzle of a life.', NULL, 'PlayStation 4', 'IGDB', 'IGDB', 'M', '0000-00-00', 'https://www.igdb.com/games/syberia-the-world-before', 'IGDB', '2021-06-01 15:13:40', '2021-06-01 15:13:40'),
(203, 388, '9 Years of Shadows', NULL, 0, 'co2thu', '9 Years of Shadows is an emotionally-driven metroidvania enhanced by healing music that tells the story of Europa, a young woman of noble birth tasked with ending the curse that plagues her people and restoring color to all lands.', NULL, 'Nintendo Switch', 'IGDB', 'IGDB', 'M', '0000-00-00', 'https://www.igdb.com/games/9-years-of-shadows', 'IGDB', '2021-06-01 15:15:00', '2021-06-01 15:15:00'),
(204, 389, 'Ruined King: A League of Legends Story', NULL, 0, 'co2jtl', 'Ruined King: A League of Legends Story is a story-driven, turn based role-playing game (RPG) being developed by Airship Syndicate and published by Riot Forge.\n\nSet after the events of Burning Tides, players will take control of LoL champions and explore the bustling city of Bilgewater and the mysterious Shadow Isles in a game for the first time.\n\nFeaturing fan favorite champions, innovative turn-based combat, and beautiful art direction along with brand new surprises and plenty of poros, Ruined King: A League of Legends Story advances the stories of many champions in the LoL Universe and offers an exciting new way to experience the World of Runeterra.', NULL, 'Xbox Series', 'IGDB', 'IGDB', 'M', '0000-00-00', 'https://www.igdb.com/games/ruined-king-a-league-of-legends-story', 'IGDB', '2021-06-01 15:20:05', '2021-06-01 15:20:05'),
(205, 390, 'Scorn', NULL, 0, 'co1r6s', 'Scorn is an atmospheric first person horror adventure game set in a nightmarish universe of odd forms and somber tapestry. It is designed around an idea of \"being thrown into the world\". Isolated and lost inside this dream-like world you will explore different interconnected regions in a non-linear fashion. The unsettling environment is a character itself. Every location contains its own theme (story), puzzles and characters that are integral in creating a cohesive lived in world. Throughout the game you will open up new areas, acquire different skill sets, weapons, various items and try to comprehend the sights presented to you.', NULL, 'PC (Microsoft Windows)', 'IGDB', 'IGDB', 'M', '0000-00-00', 'https://www.igdb.com/games/scorn', 'IGDB', '2021-06-01 15:48:28', '2021-06-01 15:48:28'),
(206, 391, 'Scorn', NULL, 0, 'co1r6s', 'Scorn is an atmospheric first person horror adventure game set in a nightmarish universe of odd forms and somber tapestry. It is designed around an idea of \"being thrown into the world\". Isolated and lost inside this dream-like world you will explore different interconnected regions in a non-linear fashion. The unsettling environment is a character itself. Every location contains its own theme (story), puzzles and characters that are integral in creating a cohesive lived in world. Throughout the game you will open up new areas, acquire different skill sets, weapons, various items and try to comprehend the sights presented to you.', NULL, 'Xbox Series', 'IGDB', 'IGDB', 'M', '0000-00-00', 'https://www.igdb.com/games/scorn', 'IGDB', '2021-06-01 15:49:04', '2021-06-01 15:49:04'),
(207, 392, 'Frozenheim', NULL, 0, 'co30gx', 'Frozenheim is a serene Norse city builder with elaborate management gameplay and RTS tactical combat. Lead your Viking clan through hardships of the frozen north, season by season, year after year. Build and survive. Set sail, explore and conquer. Win Odin’s favor and secure your place in Valhalla!', NULL, 'PC (Microsoft Windows)', 'IGDB', 'IGDB', 'M', '0000-00-00', 'https://www.igdb.com/games/frozenheim', 'IGDB', '2021-06-01 16:00:10', '2021-06-01 16:00:10'),
(208, 393, 'Psychonauts 2', NULL, 0, 'co1sod', 'Psychonauts 2 is a mind-bending trip through the strange worlds hiding inside our brains. Freshly-minted special agent and acrobat extraordinaire Razputin “Raz” Aquato returns to unpack emotional baggage and expand mental horizons. Along the way he’ll help new friends, like this magical mote of light voiced (and sung) by Jack Black. Raz must use his powers to unravel dark mysteries about the Psychonauts team and his own family origins.', NULL, 'PlayStation 4', 'IGDB', 'IGDB', 'M', '0000-00-00', 'https://www.igdb.com/games/psychonauts-2', 'IGDB', '2021-06-01 16:02:06', '2021-06-01 16:02:06'),
(209, 394, 'Torchlight III', NULL, 32, 'co2t2f', 'Set in the same beloved universe as Torchlight I and II, this shared-world action-RPG brings back many of the franchise’s signature features and mechanics that captured the hearts of ARPG fans around the world. Led by former Runic Games and Blizzard North co-founder, Max Schaefer, the team developing Torchlight Frontiers is comprised of veteran developers who were responsible for the games that defined the ARPG genre, including the original Diablo and Torchlight franchises. \n \nTorchlight Frontiers combines the heart of the beloved Torchlight series with a shared, persistent and dynamically generated world. In true Torchlight style, players will team up with friends and devoted pets to hack and slack their way through a vibrant world, discover ancient ruins of lost civilizations and brave dungeons filled with riches and dangerous creatures.', NULL, 'Nintendo Switch', 'IGDB', 'IGDB', 'M', '0000-00-00', 'https://www.igdb.com/games/torchlight-iii', 'IGDB', '2021-06-01 16:18:51', '2021-06-01 16:18:51'),
(210, 395, 'GRIME', NULL, 0, 'co2fm6', 'Explore a surreal world obsessed with proportions and anatomy, in this 2.5D Metroidvania action RPG, where you will find out what you\'re made of... and break everything else apart.', NULL, 'PC (Microsoft Windows)', 'IGDB', 'IGDB', 'M', '0000-00-00', 'https://www.igdb.com/games/grime', 'IGDB', '2021-06-01 16:22:04', '2021-06-01 16:22:04'),
(211, 396, 'Back 4 Blood', NULL, 0, 'co2mhj', 'Back 4 Blood is a thrilling cooperative first-person shooter from the creators of the critically acclaimed Left 4 Dead franchise. You are at the center of a war against the Ridden. These once-human hosts of a deadly parasite have turned into terrifying creatures bent on devouring what remains of civilization. With humanity’s extinction on the line, it’s up to you and your friends to take the fight to the enemy, eradicate the Ridden, and reclaim the world.', NULL, 'PlayStation 4', 'IGDB', 'IGDB', 'M', '0000-00-00', 'https://www.igdb.com/games/back-4-blood', 'IGDB', '2021-06-01 23:37:47', '2021-06-01 23:37:47'),
